/*============================================================================*/
/*                                                                            */
/*                                                                            */
/*                          Digital Scratch Library                           */
/*                   A motion detector for vinyl turntable                    */
/*                                                                            */
/*                                                                            */
/*============================================================================*/



-- Building requirements ----------------------------------------------------------------

[GNU/Linux]
- GCC (g++-4.x): http://gcc.gnu.org/
- Qt SDK (qt4.x): http://qt.nokia.com/downloads

[Ubuntu 11.04]
- build-essential
- qt-sdk (only qt4-dev-tools is mandatory)

[MS Windows]
- TODO


-- Build -----------------------------------------------------------------------

[GNU/Linux]
- qmake
- make
- make install

[MS Windows]
- TODO
